spanGrp.span: When we come to Buenos Aires, you coming from Germany,
Jee sa bete Buenos_Aires ra bas bete Alemania wa
You come and look for a place called Zona Sur, near Buenos Aires, Puntarenas.
Bas bete bas t k' yule k' (_) k' kie Sona Sur Buenos_Aires wa Puntarenas
There you ask those we call alligators,
Jeska / bas t tlkwa w/ sa t kie-g-ra
that is the police, you ask them for the address
polisia-wa bas t (_) ala direksion chage
There Ujarraz is located directly upwards from Buenos Aires;
Jeska ra Ujarras ra je ala Bueno(r) Buenos_Aires ska awsiga juigweta
you come toward the Talamanca mountain range, our home.
Sa k' (eh) kordillera Talamanka (_) bas bt jeska
From Buenos Aires you take the road near the school,
Buenos_Aires wa bas bt yabla yur-g kenga wa
Je wa bas bt-g bas tebeli_yaga inga ra
take the road from Salitre to Ujarraz.
bas t guge ala damu Salitre wa ala mu- m ji Ujarras wa
There it is written on cement how far it is to Ujarraz.
Jeska tl kit-l yayiga jrga Ujarras bik ki she- n ra
Jee juyukwo ts ke-l jem jiebi
You come through the savannah, long ago it was a savannah,
Jeska bas bt sk k' jira sk
but now people turned it into a pinapple plantation;
jera jiwa ra pe t kbcha r je r pia eb wa
you go by the side, or in the middle.
Jewa bas bt k kagrei wa k shawa bas bt
There is an intersection called Olan,
and you take the Ujarraz road.
You go headwards to the riverside;
tsabataga bas d Biks k wa
after the Ceibo River you go by the savannah upwards;
Biks ska bas bt juigweta k' ki eb Je ska bas bt juigweta
by the road there are some white peoples houses.
There is what in the white mans language you call puente;
jkwa ala wa jeska shk-gl sikwa kt wa kie puente blali
once you cross over you are already in the place called Ujarraz;
jeska bas kj-ra je ra bas ts-ka se je ki jrga k' kie Ujarras
there is the school in the middle,
Jera jeska eskuela jatan'-w sha ska
the church is on the left-hand side,
iglesia jatan'-w sha wa jula shul wa
where kids are taught to await God.
You can go wherever you want.
Jeska m bas shka-gle jeska bas m bas t chage
